libschrift
------------------------------------------
libschrift is a lightweight TrueType font rendering library.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libschrift-devel-0.10.2-1bl1
  libschrift0-0.10.2-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tomolt/libschrift

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tomolt/libschrift/archive/refs/tags/v0.10.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libschrift-0.10.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libschrift-0.10.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libschrift-0.10.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libschrift-0.10.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libschrift0-0.10.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libschrift-devel-0.10.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libschrift)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libschrift.README
  /usr/share/doc/libschrift/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libschrift/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/libschrift/TODO.md

(libschrift0)
  /usr/bin/cygschrift-0.dll

(libschrift-devel)
  /usr/include/schrift.h
  /usr/lib/libschrift.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libschrift.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/schrift.3.gz

------------------

